        <updateDate>2019-04-15T21:05:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Inspector General Recommendation Transparency Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Inspector General Act of 1978 to require the Council of Inspectors General on Integrity and Efficiency to establish and operate a public database of open Inspector General recommendations on which corrective action has not been completed within one year of issuance.</p>  ]]></text>
      </summary>
